Interface IClientServerOperationMapping

    IEntity

    public interface IClientServerOperationMapping
extends IEntity
    IClientServerOperationMapping: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    Defines the mapping of two particular ClientServerOperations in context of two different ClientServerInterfaces.
